12:
Phew... Think that was the last of
'em...
15:
I've lost track of all the golems we've
felled...
19:
Why do you think they stole the
presents in the first place?
21:
There is no saying what goes
through the mind of a monster... if
anything at all.
23:
What if all they wanted was to join
the celebrations?
26: They are beasts, Alk. Not children.
29:
Yeah, you're probably right... Well,
guess we better tell Lilie the deed's
done.
42:
This is one of my favorite
possessions. I offer it to you.
55: Looks fun! I want to play too!
59:
No, uh, Challua... We aren't exactly
playing here...
63:
I can help! You're looking for the
perfect present, right, Alk?
71: Then Challua knows just what to do!
81: Is this the power of sprites?!
85:
He says he's waiting for the magic
words!
102:
Heh. Guess golems want to
celebrate the holidays, just like we
do. That's kinda cute.
104:
Stella, Challua. Thanks for reaching
out to them.
112:
Now, what say we go tell Lilie the
tale of our Not-So-Silent Night?
